<h2><a name=semantic></a>Semantic-first</h2>
<p>
Stop doing this:
<pre>
&lt;div class="btn-group" role="group" ... &gt;
&lt;button type="button" class="button button-primary"&gt;
...</pre>
Start doing this
<pre>
&lt;menu&gt;
&lt;button&gt;
...</pre>
</p>

<h2><a name=classlast></a>Class-last</h2>
<p>Only variantes and utilities are acceptable classes</p>

<h2>CSS</h2>
<ul>
<li>x No LESS/SASS preprocessor.</li>
<li>x No <a href="https://medium.com/p/9a8cb347c5b5">NPM</a> requirement for building.</li>
<li>x No <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.3/getting-started/javascript/">JS-dependant</a> components.</li>
<li>v Use pure vanilla CSS.</li>
<li>v CSS variables.</li>
</ul>

